  "title": "Business Development Manager (Hydraulic Product)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Promote and develop repeat business for products (e.g., hoses, fittings) and related services</li>\n  <li>Identify, follow up on, and secure sales opportunities with a focus on long-term, repeatable revenue growth</li>\n  <li>Foster strong client relationships to support the introduction and upselling of additional product lines</li>\n  <li>Conduct purposeful sales visits to prospective clients to generate new business</li>\n  <li>Handle and respond to incoming customer inquiries effectively</li>\n  <li>Deliver product demonstrations and presentations to showcase features and benefits</li>\n  <li>Collaborate closely with the operations team to ensure product quality and timely delivery</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Business, Sales or Marketing</li>\n  <li>Experience in sales or customer relationship roles</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication, negotiation and presentation skills</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Interested applicants for the above advertised position(s), please kindly email an updated copy of your resume to: <strong>gs1@talenttradersg.com;</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA License No.: 13C6305</p>\n<p>Registration No.: R23117856 CHOE KIN MUN</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>For candidate who applied for the advertised position is deemed to have consented to us that we may collect, use or disclose your personal information for purpose in connection with the services provided by us.</p>",
